library(ggplot2)
ggplot(gapminder, aes(x=continent, y=gdpPercap)) +
  geom_point()+
  scale_y_log10()

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x=lifeExp, y=gdpPercap)) +
  geom_point(alpha=0.5)+
  scale_y_log10()

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x=continent, y=gdpPercap)) +
  geom_point(alpha=0.2)+
  geom_boxplot(alpha=0.5)+
  scale_y_log10()

ggplot(gapminder, aes(gdpPercap)) +
  geom_histogram()+
  stat_bin(bins = 50)+
  scale_y_log10()
